Introduction

Oh Seung Hee is the Main Vocalist and eldest member of the girl group CLC. She was the former leader of the group but stepped down to focus on her vocals. Her representative fruit in the group is Green Apple.

She debuted as a member of CLC on March 19, 2015, with the group's first mini album "First Love".

On March 20, 2024, Cube Entertainment announced that Seunghee's contract with them had been terminated following its expiration.
